    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "The swell is meant to be dropping today - there should be a potential for a wave or two. I hear Lorenzo’s voice in the morning talking about going surfing but I’m in no rush, so I turn over and allow a sleep in to happen. ",
            "link": null
          },
