    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Once up I take a coffee down to the point and watch Jude, Dom and Lorenzo trade a few waves in pretty average conditions. The point is not working but they are sitting on the beach break section getting a few shorter waves. It doesn’t entice me so I opt for some reading and writing instead. ",
            "link": null
          },
