    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Lina, Elly, Keegan and Jeandre join us and start an even later crayfish potjie. We haven’t all really hung out together before but it’s lovely. I play music through the speaker, initially unsure how it was going to go down - but Lina seems to know all my music and gives a lot of compliments. ",
            "link": null
          },
