          "plain_text": "Neil arrives and is immediately a huge character. After a few minutes of his truly ridiculous tales and inappropriate jokes I realise that he has almost exactly the same sense of humor as the rather dubious insurance salesman that I met in Port St Johns named Dean. When I tell him about his resemblance to Dean, he replies with something that I imagine Dean would too: “does Dean also have a great ass?”",
          "href": null
        }
      ],
      "color": "default"
