          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "He goes on a ten or so minute tangent about how having a nice ass leads to a comfortable sitting experience he then starts to get a little dark. He’s just had a bit of a meltdown and he says that Mdumbi is his safe space. It takes quite a few questions before I manage to break his spiral and get him talking about more positive things that he enjoys. ",
